urich combined with my oci always free shapes so what will come out and their affiliate links??\",\n30:       \"timestamp\": \"2026-06-14\"\n31:     },\n32:     {\n33:       \"turn\": 4,\n34:       \"role\": \"assistant\",\n35:       \"type\": \"deep_research\",\n36:       \"content_summary\": \"Comprehensive analysis of Odoo Community vs Enterprise payroll, Swiss payroll complexity (AHV/BVG/ALV/UVG/FAK/Quellensteuer/Lohnausweis — 26 cantons with different rates), UK PAYE/RTI compliance gaps, Zurich data centre free tiers (OCI eu-zurich-1, Azure Switzerland North, GCP europe-west6), Odoo partner program commissions (10-20% Enterprise, 50% Odoo.sh), and Manufact payroll value proposition. Concluded Odoo Community on OCI Always Free saves Manufact ~$14K/yr vs EORs.\",\n37:       \"urls_visited\": [\n38:         \"https://www.odoo.com/documentation/18.0/applications/hr/payroll.html\",\n39:         \"https://www.odoo.com/documentation/saas-18.4/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations.html\",\n40:         \"https://www.odoo.com/documentation/18.0/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.html\",\n41:         \"https://apps.odoo.com/apps/modules/18.0/hr_payroll_community\",\n42:         \"https://apps.odoo.com/apps/modules/18.0/xf_payroll_system\",\n43:         \"https://www.odoo.com/documentation/19.0/applications/hr/payroll.html\",\n44:         \"https://www.braincuber.com/tutorial/odoo-18-payroll-module-overview-guide\",\n45:         \"https://www.netilligence.io/blog/overview-of-payroll-management-system-in-odoo-18/\",\n46:         \"https://ecosire.com/blog/odoo-payroll-module-guide\",\n47:         \"https://arsalanyasin.com.au/odoo-18-community-vs-enterprise-in-hr/\",\n48:         \"https://www.odoo.com/page/editions\",\n49:         \"https://www.softomatesolutions.com/blog/odoo-hr-module-uk-businesses-2026/\",\n50:         \"https://www.techultrasolutions.com/compare/odoo-community-vs-enterprise\",\n51:         \"https://apps.odoo.com/apps/modules/19.0/sh_hr_payroll\"