      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Now I understand the context. Let me add a \"Why this exists\" section that ties the FreeStyle Libre reader to the health data liberation story. This should go right after \"The Problem\" section to give personal context before the technical solution.\n\nThe user has:\n- Type C blood malformation, anemia, vitamin D deficiency (from opencode.md)\n- Uses FreeStyle Libre 2 for glucose monitoring\n- Built this project to liberate their own health data\n\nI'll add a compelling \"Why this exists\" section that connects the personal health data story to the broader AI session data problem.",
