fication settings\n-   [Fork 0](/login?return_to=%2Fandiekobbietks%2FAgentSON)\n-   [Star 0](/login?return_to=%2Fandiekobbietks%2FAgentSON)\n    \n\n-   [Code](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON)\n-   [Issues 0](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/issues)\n-   [Pull requests 5](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/pulls)\n-   [Actions](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/actions)\n-   [Projects](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/projects)\n-   [Security and quality 0](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/security)\n-   [Insights](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/pulse)\n\nAdditional navigation options\n\n-   [Code](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON)\n-   [Issues](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/issues)\n-   [Pull requests](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/pulls)\n-   [Actions](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/actions)\n-   [Projects](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/projects)\n-   [Security and quality](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/security)\n-   [Insights](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/pulse)\n\n [](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON)\n\n# andiekobbietks/AgentSON\n\n master\n\n[Branches](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/branches)[Tags](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tags)\n\n[](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/branches)[](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tags)\n\nGo to file\n\nCode\n\nOpen more actions menu\n\n## Folders and files\n\nName\n\nName\n\nLast commit message\n\nLast commit date\n\n## Latest commit\n\n## History\n\n[26 Commits](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/commits/master/)\n\n[](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/commits/master/)26 Commits\n\n[SOPs](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/SOPs \"SOPs\")\n\n[SOPs](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/SOPs \"SOPs\")\n\n[cli](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/cli \"cli\")\n\n[cli](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/cli \"cli\")\n\n[docs](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/docs \"docs\")\n\n[docs](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/docs \"docs\")\n\n[exporters](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/exporters \"exporters\")\n\n[exporters](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/exporters \"exporters\")\n\n[importers](/andiekobbietks/AgentSON/tree/master/importers \"importers\")\n\