      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user wants me to continue creating the wiki content. I've created Home, Getting-Started, Schema, Readers, ADRs, and SOPs pages. Now I need to create the remaining wiki pages: Coding-Standards, Mental-Models, and Contributing.",
